<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>代理监控告警</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 800px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #d32f2f;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px 5px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 0 0 5px 5px;
        }
        .summary {
            background-color: #fff;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 10px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #2196f3;
        }
        .proxy-item {
            background-color: #fff;
            margin: 10px 0;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border-left: 4px solid #ff9800;
        }
        .proxy-healthy {
            border-left-color: #4caf50;
        }
        .proxy-unhealthy {
            border-left-color: #f44336;
        }
        .test-details {
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        .status-success {
            color: #4caf50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .status-failed {
            color: #f44336;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px;
            background-color: #e0e0e0;
            border-radius: 5px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.9em;
            color: #666;
        }
        table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
        th, td {
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #ddd;
        }
        th {
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>🚨 代理监控告警</h1>
        <p>告警时间: {{ alert_timestamp }}</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <div class="summary">
            <h2>📊 监控汇总</h2>
            <p><strong>监控代理总数:</strong> {{ alert_results | length }}</p>
            <p><strong>异常代理:</strong> {{ alert_results.values() | selectattr('status', 'equalto', 'UNHEALTHY') | list | length }}</p>
            <p><strong>健康代理:</strong> {{ alert_results.values() | selectattr('status', 'equalto', 'HEALTHY') | list | length }}</p>
            <p><strong>告警阈值:</strong> 成功率低于 {{ monitoring.thresholds.min_success_rate }}%</p>
        </div>

        <h2>🔍 代理状态详情</h2>
        {% for proxy_name, proxy_data in alert_results.items() %}
        <div class="proxy-item {{ 'proxy-healthy' if proxy_data.status == 'HEALTHY' else 'proxy-unhealthy' }}">
            <h3>
                {% if proxy_data.status == 'HEALTHY' %}
                    ✅ {{ proxy_name }}
                {% else %}
                    ❌ {{ proxy_name }}
                {% endif %}
            </h3>
            <p><strong>代理地址:</strong> {{ proxy_data.proxy_url }}</p>
            <p><strong>状态:</strong> 
                <span class="{{ 'status-success' if proxy_data.status == 'HEALTHY' else 'status-failed' }}">
                    {{ '健康' if proxy_data.status == 'HEALTHY' else '异常' }}
                </span>
            </p>
            <p><strong>成功率:</strong> {{ proxy_data.success_rate }}%</p>
            <p><strong>测试结果:</strong> {{ proxy_data.successful_tests }}/{{ proxy_data.total_tests }} 成功</p>
            
            <div class="test-details">
                <h4>📋 测试详情:</h4>
                <table>
                    <tr>
                        <th>网站</th>
                        <th>地址</th>
                        <th>状态</th>
                        <th>响应时间(ms)</th>
                        <th>HTTP状态码</th>
                    </tr>
                    {% for test in proxy_data.test_details %}
                    <tr>
                        <td>{{ test.website }}</td>
                        <td>{{ test.url }}</td>
                        <td class="{{ 'status-success' if test.status == 'SUCCESS' else 'status-failed' }}">
                            {{ '成功' if test.status == 'SUCCESS' else '失败' }}
                        </td>
                        <td>{{ test.response_time if test.response_time != -1 else '无' }}</td>
                        <td>{{ test.status_code if test.status_code != -1 else '无' }}</td>
                    </tr>
                    {% endfor %}
                </table>
            </div>
        </div>
        {% endfor %}

        <div class="summary">
            <h2>🔧 建议操作</h2>
            <ul>
                {% for proxy_name, proxy_data in alert_results.items() %}
                    {% if proxy_data.status == 'UNHEALTHY' %}
                <li><strong>{{ proxy_name }}:</strong> 检查代理服务器连通性和配置</li>
                    {% endif %}
                {% endfor %}
                <li>查看代理服务器日志获取详细错误信息</li>
                <li>验证监控系统与代理服务器之间的网络连通性</li>
                <li>检查代理认证凭据是否有效</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>此告警由 Ansible 代理监控系统自动生成</p>
        <p>详细信息请查看监控日志: {{ monitoring.logging.log_dir }}/{{ monitoring.logging.log_file }}</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>